data.description: Brand New Roof!  Come and check out this beautifully maintained 2 bedrooms, 2 bath Villa located in the highly desired Sun City Center. This home features plenty of living space including a large, enclosed Florida room. The primary bedroom features en-suite, separate vanity area and a walk-in closet. The secondary bedroom has a view overlooking a rock garden and plenty of natural light. Kitchen includes granite countertops, refrigerator, stove, built in oven and dishwasher. Large great room and dining room for plenty of entertainment. Home also includes a large laundry area and storage room. Come and be a part of the active community of Sun City Center. Freshly painted bedrooms, hallway, dining and living room.  The two-car carport can be converted into an enclosed garage with entry through both the carport door and laundry room door.  Additional $10K flex cash at closing towards upgrades (i.e., garage enclosure, kitchen, bathroom, or screened porch enclosure) with full asking price of $260K.
